                <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.J.28.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 21, paragraph 8</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian"
                        notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00"
                        >undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>At the end of Article 21 add a new paragraph 8, worded as follows: <quote
                        rend="blockquote">
                        <p>8. “<hi rend="italic">Any instrument drawn up or contract concluded
                                during the war on occupied territory between Greek and Bulgarian
                                nationals, purporting to transfer Greek property, subsequently
                                removed to Bulgaria, shall be null and void</hi>.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
